                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini dei aeterni. <persName ref="#people/173"
                            key="#Emperor/king">Otto</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">rex</rs>. Si petitionibus fidelium nostrorum
                        libenter annuimus, fideliores eos nobis esse minime dubitamus. Quocirca
                        omnium universalis eclesie fidelium nostrorum videlicet presentium ac
                        futurorum noverit industria, qualiter <persName ref="#people/1301"
                            key="#Queen">Hadeleida</persName> dilecta coniunx nostra et <persName
                            ref="#people/1611" key="#Marquis/duke">Chonradus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> fidelissimus noster nostram suppliciter
                        exoraverunt magestatem, quatenus ob amorem superne remunerationis per
                        nostram precepti paginam quodam <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterium</rs>
                        infra <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/43" key="#Cities">Placentinam</placeName> a beate
                        memorie <persName ref="#people/55" key="#Queen">Angelberga</persName>
                        videlicet <rs key="#Queen">imperatrice</rs> constructum et in honore
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/53" key="#Monasteries">sancti
                            Sixti</orgName> dedicatum <persName ref="#people/67" key="#Abbesses"
                            >Berte</persName> nobilissime <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatisse</rs> nobis
                        devotissime cum omnibus suis pertinentiis confirmare dignaremur, simul
                        quoque roborantes et in perpetuum concedentes eidem monasterio quasdam <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curtes</rs>, <geogName ref="#estates/40"
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/33"
                                key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                >Uuardasstallum</placeName></geogName> scilicet, <geogName
                            ref="#estates/110"
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/141"
                                key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                >Campum Miliatio</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            ref="#estates/207"
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/462"
                                key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                >Curte noua</placeName></geogName>, <geogName ref="#estates/112"
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/354"
                                key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                >Sexto</placeName></geogName>, <geogName ref="#estates/38"
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/32"
                                key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                >Luciariam</placeName></geogName>, <geogName ref="#estates/77"
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/361"
                                key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                >Litora paludiana</placeName></geogName>, <geogName
                            ref="#estates/80"
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/362"
                                key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                >Uillole</placeName></geogName>, <geogName ref="#estates/42"
                            key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                ><placeName ref="#places/34"
                                key="#Houses #Rivers #Shores #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Castle #Markets #Districtio #Churches/religious_bodies #Aldius #Royal_slave"
                                >Piguniariam</placeName></geogName> cum agecentiis eorum, et omnia
                        quecumque memorata imperatrix per <rs key="#Testamentum">institutionis sue
                            paginam</rs> ubique idem cenobium diffinivit habendum. Quorum
                        petitionibus tota devotione faventes id fieri annuimus, hoc nostrum
                        preceptum scribi iubentes per quod prelibate Berte abbatisse idem
                        monasterium confirmamus, quatenus in sua sit potestate et dominio cousque
                        vixerit, et ibidem dominatrix et ordinatrix atque rectrix invigilet donec
                        eius fuerit vita, per quod etiam iam prescriptas venerabili loco concedimus
                        ac confirmamus omnes res et posessiones mobiles ac immobiles tam per <rs
                            key="#Cartula">cartulas</rs> quamque extra cartulas vel cuicum
                        inscriptionis titulo ad partem ipsius monasterii legibus adquisitas et
                        quirendas seu quicquid per regum vel imperatorum antecessorum nostrorum <rs
                            key="#Diploma">precepta</rs> ad eundem sacrum locum collatum est, atque
                            <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellulam</rs> quandam que antiquitus
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/1508" key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            >Monasterium</orgName> dicebatur, non procul a Placentine urbe scitam
                        qui <placeName ref="#places/14"
                            key="#Cells/hermitages#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >Caput Trebie</placeName> vocatur, in qua <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1503"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >eclesia apostolorum principis</orgName> honore dicata consistit, cum
                        omnibus inibi pertinentibus quemadmodum Carllomannus serenissimus rex
                        antiquitus eandem cellulam cum universis suis appendiciis eidem monasterio
                            <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario iure</rs> largitus
                        est, prenominato venerabili loco per hoc nostre regalis auctoritatis
                        preceptum ex integro perdonamus largimur confirmamus ac modis omnibus
                        corroboramus, familas quoque utriusque sexus et condicionibus cum [c]urtibus
                        et <rs key="#Churches/religious_bodies">capellis</rs> earumque appendiciis,
                        cum omnibus <rs key="#Castle">castellis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pascuis</rs> pratis <rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>
                        salectis sationibus paludbus aquis aquarumque decursibus <rs key="#Mills"
                            >molendinis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Rivers">fluminibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Shores">ripis</rs> rupinis <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs>
                        collibus vallibus ac planitiebus cultis et incultis divisis et indivisis <rs
                            key="#Markets">mercationibus</rs> vectigalibus <rs key="#Districtio"
                            >districtionibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Royal_slave">servis et ancillis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Aldius">alldiis et aldianis</rs> et omnibus que dici aut nominari
                        possunt, ad idem monasterium iuxte et legaliter respicientibus in integrum
                        confirmamus, ita videlicet ut prelibata Berta abbatissa quousque vixerit ac
                        nostra auctoritate roborata de prescriptis rebus eidem monasterio
                        pertinentibus tam per preceptorum paginam ut diximus quamque aliarum
                        instrumenta cartarum et adquisitis et adquirendis potestative fatiat,
                        magnarum parvarumque personarum moletatione remota. Si quis huius nostri
                        precepti infringere voluerit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri
                            optimi libras centum</rs>, medietatem <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere
                            nostre</rs> et medietatem prefate abbatissae. Et ut hoc verius credatur
                        et atentius observetur, manu nostra propria signatum et anuli nostri subter
                        iussimus adfirmari. Signum domni Ottonis serenissimi regis (MF.)  <persName
                            key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Vulgifridus">Uuigfridus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> advicem <persName ref="#people/175"
                            key="#Archchaplain">Brunonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Archchaplain">archicappellani</rs> recognovi. (SI. D.)   Data
                        VIII. idus februa. anno incarnationis domini Iesu Christi DCCCCLII,
                        indictione X, anno vero domni Ottonis in Italia I, in Francia XVI; actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/65">Papia</placeName>; feliciter in dei nomine
                        amen.</ab>
